{"id": 2411, "genre": 1000, "title": "日常听歌，你都是怎么挑选歌曲的？", "description": "你的音乐筛选人格都是哪种？（题图来自：istock ©VectorFun ）", "record_count": 24280, "comment_count": 86, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/2018061117372173PGTnI4zK1JsmoH.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-06-13T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 4365, "title": "日常听歌，你都是怎么挑选歌曲的？", "content": "日常听歌，你都是怎么挑选歌曲的?", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 286535, "content": "歌手跟随型，喜欢的歌手会去搜专辑来听", "image": "img/option/option/20180611173849J37OIBPSiZTcQEG8.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 286536, "content": "场景搜索型，根据需要搜跑步、睡觉、看书场景音乐", "image": "img/option/option/20180611173921k8Re9Mq4xUHXCSKd.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 286542, "content": "应用调教型，固定好风格以后基本上都听“猜你喜欢”", "image": "img/option/option/201806111745071FXtaIcWxyplVOC8.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 286543, "content": "学习鉴赏型，系统地找经典音乐来听，乐手/曲目信息都会注意", "image": "img/option/option/201806111746377v3mwPuhQTiGMOFj.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 286548, "content": "老歌循环型，总是重复播放曲库里下载的那些单曲", "image": "img/option/option/20180611175405KI1xrgN537J8kuX6.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 286551, "content": "榜单推荐型，音乐应用排行榜上的、评论数999+的歌都会更想听", "image": "img/option/option/20180611175504A5hguIO8kXfBoT9s.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 286555, "content": "随机探索型，各种风格的音乐都会尝试，歌单名或封面不错就会听听", "image": "img/option/option/20180611175608X1IKnqrluEPpba5U.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 286557, "content": "活动需要型，要去音乐节/音乐会了才开始补听", "image": "img/option/option/20180611175806mb0c6HCnlipYsFMP.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 286559, "content": "几乎不听型，不会专门去找音乐听", "image": "img/option/option/20180611180114yv2osINShQmfbg8B.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 286561, "content": "友邻分享型，看到好友发的音乐都会点开听听看", "image": "img/option/option/20180611180205tbMeVONyfoCHErBp.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 286932, "content": "综艺洗脑型，歌单跟着热门音乐综艺走", "image": "img/option/option/20180613093208h2vBpVcHdw9OLjlg.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}